  "text": "The details for RNA extraction, microarray, qPCR protocol, and milk yield and composition are reported in Additional file S3. Briefly, we used an annotated bovine oligonucleotide microarray containing .10,000 unique elements [CITATION_1] . Hybridizations were performed in a dye-swap reference design. The microarray data presented in this manuscript have been deposited at NCBI's Gene Expression Omnibus [CITATION_2] and are accessible through GEO Series accession number GSE19055.",
